      "title": "Railway fares increased from tonight (22)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Railways announced that the Railway fares will be increased with effect from midnight today (22).",
        "According to a gazette notification, the minimum fare has been increased from Rs.10/- to 20/-.",
        "General Kamal Gunaratne (Retd) reappointed as the Secretary of Defence"
